  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🌾 Create, Cultivate, Profit!</h2><br>You've inherited your grandfather's farm, which has been reduced to a lone island amidst a relentless sea. With nothing but a deck of cards and the entrepreneurial spirit, you are tasked to pay off a mounting debt, turning this desolate patch of land into a thriving agrarian empire.<br><br><strong>Each card you play represents different elements of your farm - from the crops you sow, the animals you raise, to the structures you build.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2464880/extras/9fa6ae5d4a80f1d0ecb0260acb93dbc7.poster.avif?t=1768253121\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2464880/extras/9fa6ae5d4a80f1d0ecb0260acb93dbc7.webm?t=1768253121\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2464880/extras/9fa6ae5d4a80f1d0ecb0260acb93dbc7.mp4?t=1768253121\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >💰 Choose, Produce, Profit!</h2><br>Every few turns choose between unique cards, and buffs<br><br>Generate items each turn, sell them for cash, and invest this money to expand your farm, pay off fees, and gradually chip away at the enormous debt.<br><strong>the challenge is to maximize efficiency and make as much money as possible.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2464880/extras/fb08c53bcbdce9f753b3351ce696a392.poster.avif?t=1768253121\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2464880/extras/fb08c53bcbdce9f753b3351ce696a392.webm?t=1768253121\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2464880/extras/fb08c53bcbdce9f753b3351ce696a392.mp4?t=1768253121\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🌾 Create, Cultivate, Profit!</h2><br>You've inherited your grandfather's farm, which has been reduced to a lone island amidst a relentless sea. With nothing but a deck of cards and the entrepreneurial spirit, you are tasked to pay off a mounting debt, turning this desolate patch of land into a thriving agrarian empire.<br><br><strong>Each card you play represents different elements of your farm - from the crops you sow, the animals you raise, to the structures you build.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2464880/extras/9fa6ae5d4a80f1d0ecb0260acb93dbc7.poster.avif?t=1768253121\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2464880/extras/9fa6ae5d4a80f1d0ecb0260acb93dbc7.webm?t=1768253121\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2464880/extras/9fa6ae5d4a80f1d0ecb0260acb93dbc7.mp4?t=1768253121\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >💰 Choose, Produce, Profit!</h2><br>Every few turns choose between unique cards, and buffs<br><br>Generate items each turn, sell them for cash, and invest this money to expand your farm, pay off fees, and gradually chip away at the enormous debt.<br><strong>the challenge is to maximize efficiency and make as much money as possible.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2464880/extras/fb08c53bcbdce9f753b3351ce696a392.poster.avif?t=1768253121\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2464880/extras/fb08c53bcbdce9f753b3351ce696a392.webm?t=1768253121\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.st